.TH "kvm_vz_should_use_htimer" 9 "kvm_vz_should_use_htimer" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
kvm_vz_should_use_htimer \- Find whether to use the VZ hard guest timer.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" kvm_vz_should_use_htimer
.BI "(struct kvm_vcpu *vcpu "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "vcpu" 12
Virtual CPU.
.SH "RETURN"
true if the VZ GTOffset & real guest CP0_Count should be used
instead of software emulation of guest timer.
false otherwise.
